  <h3>Create a project</h3>
    For project management, the user is provided with a complete implementation of EVM Earned Value Management.
    <br/>
    <p><br/>
    Earned Value Management, also known as EVM, is a methodology that describes the project status, evaluating the project progress and performance, when processing information obtained from the scope measures, timeline and resources.
    </p>

